          <h3 class="info-title">What is LBM?</h3>
          <p class="info-text">Lean Body Mass is the total weight of your body minus fat tissue. It includes your muscles, vital skeletal bones, essential organs, vascular fluids, skin, and structural water.</p>
        </div>
        <div class="info-card">
          <div class="info-icon" style="background:rgba(99,102,241,0.1);color:#6366f1">
            <svg width="24" height="24" viewBox="0 0 24 24" fill="none" stroke="currentColor" stroke-width="2"><rect x="3" y="3" width="18" height="18" rx="2"/><path d="M9 3v18M15 3v18"/></svg>
